verbose_text: DNMT1 mRNA expression was significantly increased in the ISDN + HG group compared to the HG group (0.82 +/-0.13 vs. 0.53 +/-0.08, P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG); DEC1 mRNA expression was decreased in the ISDN + HG group compared to the HG group (2.14 +/-0.23 vs. 3.68 +/-0.26, P < 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
